<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Thu, 12 May 2022 07:36:30 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>Android 13 正式登場，無縫藍牙音訊 + 平板顯示改良</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/12/android-13-google-io/software/android-app/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=android-13-google-io</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 12 May 2022 07:36:30 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[Android App]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1099461</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Google I/O 2022 年度開發者會議中，Android 13、Pixel 7 正式登場。全新 And [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Google I/O 2022 年度開發者會議中，Android 13、Pixel 7 正式登場。全新 Android 13 作業系統將對平板電腦裝置的大熒幕空間佈置大幅改良，善用大熒幕更有效率顯示內容。跨裝置連接也成為新系統改良重點，支援藍牙無縫切換，用戶能在多個 Android 裝置之間無縫地繼續收聽音訊內容；跨裝置剪貼簿可讓手機平板與 Chromebook 之間互傳文字、圖片、網址。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0005-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099462" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0005-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0005-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0005-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0005-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0004-1.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>Google 發表 Android 13 作業系統，其中最大重點是增強裝置之間的聯繫，Android 手機、平板實現無縫切換藍牙耳機連接，用戶可繼續在另一部裝置收聽音訊內容。率先支援此功能的耳機有 Sony、JBL 以及 Pixel 耳機。Android 13 也將配合 Chromebook 新增的「Phone Hub」應用程式，讓用戶跨裝置共享剪貼簿，在手機與電腦之間直接 Copy &amp; Paste 文字、網址、圖片等內容。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0004-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099466" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0004-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0004-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0004-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0004-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0001-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099467" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0001-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0001-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0001-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0001-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>而新系統也針對平板電腦裝置，提供更好的操作體驗，用戶可拖放目標應用程式做到分割畫面多工操作兩個應用程式，也會提供全新工具列；而超過 20 款以甘的原生 App 的操控、介面將得到改善，Google Play Store 的使用便利程度也會獲得提升。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Google-Keynote-Google-I_O-‘22-1-23-2-screenshot.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099470" src="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Google-Keynote-Google-I_O-‘22-1-23-2-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Google-Keynote-Google-I_O-‘22-1-23-2-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Google-Keynote-Google-I_O-‘22-1-23-2-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Google-Keynote-Google-I_O-‘22-1-23-2-screenshot.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0000-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099464" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0000-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0000-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0000-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0000-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在 Chromecast、Fast Pair 上新系統也將支援更多品牌的產品。系統將內建支援 Matter 智能家電標準，讓 Google Home 生態系統可得到更大擴展。</p><p>其他小改進還有用戶可個別設定每個 App 的語言、設定每個 App 推送通知的權限、支援點對點加密群組對話、支援 RCS 短訊系統、全新緊急警報系統等。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0002.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099463" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0002-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0002-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0002-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unwire0002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>已參加 Android Beta Program 的機主可透過 OTA 更新取得預覽版 Android 13，支援機種包括 Pixel 4/4 XL, Pixel 4a/4a(5G), Pixel 5/5a, Pixel 6,6 Pro。而另外有 12 個吸 ASUS Zenfone 8、Lenovo Tab P12 Pro、OPPO Find N、OPPO Find X5 Pro、OnePlus 10 Pro、小米 12、小米 12 Pro、小米平板 5、Redmi K50 Pro、Realme GT2 Pro 現在亦可安裝 Android 13 預覽版。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.androidpolice.com/android-13/">Android Police</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display:block; margin:0 auto;" width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?controls=0&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
