</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>初代 iPhone 原型機曝光    iPod 滾輪背後藏數字按鍵</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/11/iphone-prototype-2/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=iphone-prototype-2</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 11 May 2022 11:31:41 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1099164</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>在 2007 年 iPhone 發表之前，曾經有過為數不少的原型機，部份原型機成為了今時今日 iPhone 設 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>在 2007 年 iPhone 發表之前，曾經有過為數不少的原型機，部份原型機成為了今時今日 iPhone 設計的主要元素。而有兩款原型機於日前由設計者親自曝光。</p><p>最近發表這兩款 iPhone 原型機的資料是來自 Tony Fadell，他在 2000 年代主要設計 iPod 音樂播放器。當年 Apple 希望能將 iPod 移植到手提電話，Motorola 的 ROKR E1 產品就曾經加入 iTunes 功能。不過 Apple 對此機的效果並不滿意，於是便想開發自家智能手機產品。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2016-09-07-at-09.33.06.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099165" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2016-09-07-at-09.33.06-694x413.png" alt="" width="694" height="413" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2016-09-07-at-09.33.06-694x413.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2016-09-07-at-09.33.06-1280x762.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2016-09-07-at-09.33.06-768x457.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2016-09-07-at-09.33.06-1536x914.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2016-09-07-at-09.33.06.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>最初的一個設計，是在一部 iPod 的背後，加入視像鏡頭與數字鍵盤，機身表面仍然使用 iPod 的招牌旋轉滾輪。機身所採用的顏色，即銀、黑設計，被採用到後來發表的第一代 iPhone。根據 Tony Fadell 的解說，這款「iPod Phone」原型機後來由第三方生產商製造了實物出來。</p><p>Tony Fadell 指，當時 Steve Jobs 希望將電話元素加入現有的 iPod，而並非製作一部全新智能手機產品，因為他本人想保留 iPod 標誌性的旋轉滾輪。開發團隊不斷嘗試在旋轉滾輪上實現不同的輸入方式，在團隊告知 Steve Jobs 很多事情無法實現時，他仍然要求團隊「Keep trying!（繼續嘗試！）」。</p><p>不過到最後，Steve Jobs 也認為旋轉滾輪作為手機輸入的使用體驗不佳，他著令開發團隊重新思考新機的設計，今次設計就帶了巨大（以當時來說）的輕觸式顯示屏，沒有物理按鍵，搭載了像 Mac OS X 為本的系統。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/iPhone-Prototypes.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099169" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/iPhone-Prototypes-654x580.jpg" alt="" width="654" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/iPhone-Prototypes-654x580.jpg 654w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/iPhone-Prototypes-1014x900.jpg 1014w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/iPhone-Prototypes-768x681.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/iPhone-Prototypes-1536x1363.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/iPhone-Prototypes.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 654px" /></a></p><p>Tony Fadell 發表的新書「Build」透露了更多 iPhone、iPod 開發史，包括 Steve Jobs 極力反對 iPod 支援 Windows 電腦，另外也提及 Google CEO, Eric Schmidt 曾向 Steve Jobs 諫言網頁應用程式 (web apps) 可用作 iPhone 連結電腦的方式。</p><p>資料來源：9to5mac</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display:block; margin:0 auto;" width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?controls=0&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=TceJ7i8u0Vg:3tkuGOs_oFo:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=TceJ7i8u0Vg:3tkuGOs_oFo:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>DJI Mini 3 Pro 登場      香港價錢 + 詳細規格</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/11/dji-mini-3-pro/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=dji-mini-3-pro</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 11 May 2022 11:14:31 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[航拍]]></category><category><![CDATA[dji]]></category><category><![CDATA[DJI mini 3 Pro]]></category><category><![CDATA[航拍機]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1099244</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>DJI 於今日正式推出新一代 DJI Mini 3 Pro。DJI Mini 3 Pro 集輕小便攜、影像實力 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>DJI 於今日正式推出新一代 DJI Mini 3 Pro。DJI Mini 3 Pro 集輕小便攜、影像實力、避障系統、智慧功能於一身。DJI Mini 3 Pro 重量低於 249 克，延續小身形，高性能設計，搭載 1/1.3 英寸感測器，具三向環境感知能力，最長續航時間可達 47 分鐘。DJI Mini 3 Pro 創新構型在動力、避障、雲臺方面經過全新佈局，機身新增減阻設計並增大漿葉面積，大幅提升動力效能；首次前置後視避障感測器，並擴大了障礙物感知範圍，提升飛行安全體驗；雲臺經過全新規劃，可設置無損豎拍、大角度仰拍，令創作更有可塑性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099271 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ DJI Mini 3 Pro</p><p>延續前代低於 249 克的重量，DJI Mini 3 Pro 機臂摺疊方式和機身結構均經過重新設計，方便用家收納和出行輕鬆便捷。</p><h2>可達 47 分鐘續航力</h2><p>續航性能作為航拍創作的基礎，在消費級無人機中首次突破至最長 47 分鐘。全新構型設計通過改變機身傾角和增大槳葉面積，降低了風阻從而大幅提升動力效能，令 DJI Mini 3 Pro 的續航得到顯著突破。用家結合智豐飛行電池可使用長達 34 分鐘，選配長續航電池更可使用長達 47 分鐘。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099272 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新設計改變機身傾角</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099275 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲增大槳葉面積</p><h2>三向避障性能</h2><p>DJI Mini 3 Pro 具三向避障性能，是 DJI Mini 系列迄今安全性最強的無人機。其配備前視、後視、下視雙目視覺感應系統和 ToF （Time-of-Flight），得益於創新構型，障礙物感知範圍大幅提升。在此基礎上，APAS 4.0 幫助下，更好的自主路徑規劃及靈敏避障，可自動探測並躲避飛行路徑中的障礙物，在複雜場景下也能順滑飛行。</p><h2><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099277 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h2><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099278 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲首次前置後視避障感測器</p><h2>12 公里最遠傳輸距離</h2><p>DJI Mini 3 Pro 採用 DJI O3 旗艦數位圖傳。DJI Mini 3 Pro 可設置 1080p/30fps 最高實時圖傳畫質和 12 公里最遠傳輸距離，最大圖傳碼率 18Mbps，且抗幹擾能力大幅增強，進一步提升複雜拍攝場景中的圖傳可靠性。DJI Mini 3 Pro 身形雖小，其動力冗餘設計帶來最高可抗 5 級風。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099282 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 12 公里最遠傳輸距離</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099281 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最高可抗 5 級風</p><h2>1/1.3 英寸感測器加大光圈</h2><p>DJI Mini 3 Pro 在影像系統上進行了專業升級，搭載 1/1.3 英寸影像感測器，新增雙原生 ISO，支援直出 HDR 影像，更高的動態範圍令明暗部位細節得以保留。DJI Mini 3 Pro 配備了 f/1.7 大光圈鏡頭，配合感光能力 2.44μm 四合一大像素，帶來純凈透亮的夜景效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099285 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配備 f/1.7 大光圈鏡頭</p><h2>可錄製 4K/60fps 4800 萬像素 RAW 照片</h2><p>DJI Mini 3 Pro 最高可錄製 4K/60fps 影片和拍攝 4800 萬像素 RAW 格式照片。DJI Mini 3 Pro 支援 1080p/120fps 慢動作攝影，還新增 D-Cinelike 色彩模式，為創作者提供更廣闊的調整空間。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099299 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最高可錄製 4K/60fps 影片和拍攝 4800 萬像素 RAW 格式照片</p><h2>更多拍攝模式</h2><p>DJI Mini 3 Pro 首次設置無損豎拍和大角度仰拍，帶來豐富的視覺效果和多樣玩法，讓使用者更輕鬆拍攝大片。 得益於全新雲臺構型設計，DJI Mini 3 Pro 雲臺轉動限位更小，不僅能實現大角度仰拍，更支援無裁切豎拍，引領社交平臺航拍創意潮流。 DJI Mini 3 Pro 還支援焦點跟隨功能，配備智慧跟隨、聚焦、興趣點環繞三種跟拍模式，將主角始終鎖定在 C 位。大師鏡頭、延時攝影功能首次在 Mini 系列出現，讓航拍機自主完成複雜運鏡， 極大降低使用者創作門檻 。 使用者還可拍攝 180°、廣角、豎拍、球形全景照片。 此外，為提升使用者分享體驗，手機快傳功能支援 Wi-Fi 高速下載，最高速率可達 30MB/s。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099286 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲無損豎拍</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099288 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲無損豎拍</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099287 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲大角度仰拍</p><h2><strong>豐富新增配件為創作加碼</strong></h2><p>DJI 推出專為 DJI Mini 3 Pro 設計的全新輕量化帶屏遙控器 DJI RC ，內置 DJI Fly app，操作便捷高效，告別繁瑣連接，大幅提升起飛效率。 專用帶屏遙控器讓使用者無需擔心手機電量，更能專注創作。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099290 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全新輕量化帶屏遙控器 DJI RC</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099293 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099291 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099292 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08362-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08362-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08362-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08362-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08362-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08362-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08362-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099294 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08311-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08311-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08311-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08311-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08311-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08311-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08311-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>DJI 在 DJI Mini 3 Pro 上首創大小電池設計，用戶可選用 DJI Mini 3 Pro 長續航智慧飛行電池，最長續航時間達 47 分鐘 。 雙向充電管家可同時為遙控器和三塊電池依次充電，也能充當移動電源為遙控器或手機等設備充電。 使用者也可自行選配 ND 鏡套裝，以充足的準備應對日間強光下的拍攝環境，享受不同場景下的拍攝樂趣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099295 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08363-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08363-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08363-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08363-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08363-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08363-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08363-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099296 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08364-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08364-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08364-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08364-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08364-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08364-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08364-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099297 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08314-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08314-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08314-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08314-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08314-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08314-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08314-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最長續航時間達 47 分鐘</p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 96px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 48px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 48px;">DJI Mini 3 Pro 單機（配備 DJI RC-N1 標準遙控器）：</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 48px;">港幣$6,039</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">DJI Mini 3 Pro 帶屏控飛機套裝：</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港幣$7,299</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">暢飛電池套裝：</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">港幣$1,379</td></tr></tbody></table><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 50%;">暢飛長續航電池套裝：</td><td style="width: 50%;">港幣$1,879</td></tr></tbody></table><p>香港代理：OTG</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display:block; margin:0 auto;" width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?controls=0&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
